{"tid":1689924,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不如改下個口號，唔好再叫香港人 反抗","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:55:47.000Z","uid":281180,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64e43630fdaa67f16a2d0a2d81b7a864d50f1ca1","tid":1689924,"uid":281180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:22:39.000Z","msg":"唔好負評住<br />\n<br />\n我朋友成日發夢，夢境中佢聽到有人嗌 「香港人 反抗」<br />\n佢滿心歡喜向前衝，點知夢境中見到有d綠色嘅蟲係前面就後退，有人開始跑，由香港人反抗變左做香港人走佬。<br />\n<br />\n一個無法達成嘅口號，講得愈多，無力感愈大。<br />\n如果下次你叫得出呢個口號，代表你有責任去「執行」<br />\n和勇不割，但如果現場和理非多，不如試下叫一D 可以做到嘅事，例如：香港人 罷工"},{"pid":"507e6b4d05763e7c1a6a5f637fbc141bb2e9ab0b","tid":1689924,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nShare:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3162303350510828?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F454004001340790%2Fposts%2F3162303350510828%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=4b26e1af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/3162303350510828?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nRT:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/effygrande1/status/1190670210027552768?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feffygrande1%2Fstatus%2F1190670210027552768%3Fs%3D21&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=